@Robert Murray-Smith I've been following your work for a few months now; and I've just finished up a project adding an electric trolling motor to a recreation sit-it kayak--I'm set on using one of your wind/water turbines to extend/charge the travel time. I printed your vortex turbine already; but now that I"m seeing this...
